headline: Otis Chosen to Help Connect Singapore on Cross Island Line Phase 1 and Punggol Extension
summary: Otis (NYSE: OTIS), the world's leading elevator and escalator manufacturing, installation and service company, has been selected by the Land Transport Authority (LTA) to help create a seamless and user-friendly transport experience on the Singapore Mass Rail Transport (MRT)'s new Cross Island Line.

headline: 2 S&P 500 Stocks to Target This Week and 1 Facing Challenges
summary: While the S&P 500 (^GSPC) includes industry leaders, not every stock in the index is a winner. Some companies are past their prime, weighed down by poor execution, weak financials, or structural headwinds.
